00:20:35,910 --> 00:20:39,450
For those who haven't heard GLTF
before, it is a 3D file format,

497
00:20:39,450 --> 00:20:42,270
and it is a required
component of this model viewer

498
00:20:42,270 --> 00:20:44,910
because it's a format that will
allow us to work across all

499
00:20:44,910 --> 00:20:47,507
